{"tid":1567324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【力抗暴政 以善制惡】9.15 香港人行街攻略分析","createTime":"2019-09-14T04:39:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T05:02:48.000Z","uid":178013,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9d923b0198291beb0b65ddf95ac2faa28dcf4bf0","tid":1567324,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:39:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家係咪以為羸咗呀?<br />\n唔係嘅話就努力啲宣傳啦! <br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n9.15 英領<br />\n時間: 12點<br />\n<br />\n9.15 遊行<br />\n時間: 2點半<br />\n起點: 銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n終點: 遮打道行人專用區<br />\n<br />\n有幾點想講:<br />\n<br />\n1. <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins>遊行人數好重要</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n警方俾咗反對通知，如果你身邊朋友猶豫緊出唔出，甚至嗰個係你，請記住香港係有集會自由!但而家已經蕩然無存。<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人必需站出來捍衛香港嘅核心價值。Hong Kong is not China.</span><br />\n<br />\n2.<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> <ins>銀髮族扮演重要角色</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔好睇少銀髮族，佢地好關鍵! 警察其實好少搞銀髮族，所以人數多嘅話，佢地可以成為年青人嘅屏障。<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>勇武和理缺一不可</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n和理非手足請繼續和理非，因為今次遊行人數非常重要，我地要玩到五大訴求應承哂為止，絕對寸步不讓。<br />\n<br />\n勇武手足請繼續帶gear。保護好自己，保護好身邊手足，一個都不能少。隨時要準備同黑警搏鬥，但都要小心。唔好因戀戰而送頭。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武和理團結係運動繼續行落去嘅重要彈藥!</span><br />\n<br />\n4. <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins>嚴防休班警特襲</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家都如而家休班警配備警棍，隨時可以毆我地。但係我地絕對唔可以任人魚肉!<span style=\"color: red;\">所以我地需要提高警覺，千祈唔好落單。如果真係有手足俾人圍，一定要大嗌求助! 其他人務必救受困手足!</span><br />\n<br />\n5. <strong><ins>退場計劃 (Exit Plan)</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n黨鐵封站係基本動作。要順利退場，<span style=\"color: red;\">我地要變裝!將自己打扮成一個普通市民，隱藏於鬧市當中。大家遊行完可以行街、食飯、睇戲。而家唔係出街都犯法呀嘛?</span><br />\n總之盡量唔好俾啲狗有理由懷疑你參加集會。<br />\n<br />\n當大家撤緊時，和理非如果聽到有關防暴嘅消息時請保持冷静，唔好拔足狂奔，以免制造恐慌。<span style=\"color: red;\">大家可以急步行，退緊時盡量唔好嗌口號! 太嘈會傳達唔到現場訊息!!</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"93b15750e410739cf3ec3559379501a5c69e1679","tid":1567324,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hAktYu5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhAktYu5.jpg&h=af02f29f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C8SPHWL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC8SPHWL.jpg&h=e32bb121&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f0c69478172ea32e1e9bf21b908f3fbdc032644","tid":1567324,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:41:44.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"b0043fb36b70f685e6536cd66a41b78f8f2b9982","tid":1567324,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:42:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位手足聽日見！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sixL0H5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsixL0H5.jpg&h=7456f0ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cis8d25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCis8d25.jpg&h=359b5e5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c4486d44c3e44794dba16867055eda0cb68fb98","tid":1567324,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:43:19.000Z","msg":"915 見"},{"pid":"f6540c024e7d18da53a150b55a0ae302a72508fc","tid":1567324,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:43:29.000Z","msg":"915 見"},{"pid":"7e170c28227b55a5559927c47e8ffcd4971bf544","tid":1567324,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:43:56.000Z","msg":"幫推熱門"},{"pid":"d8080a2c7eb8e703f266c6ade76d576bcc3c8f61","tid":1567324,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"