r />\n《願榮光》之後。。。<br />\n天滅中共 平反六四！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">海外臨時政府 自由香港<br />\nFREE HONG KONG</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/freehongkonghkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffreehongkonghkg&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZ%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=77f18cf4\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/freehongkonghkg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/nBMTNBB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnBMTNBB.jpg&h=16392072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n讓這攬炒旗隨風飄揚！（logo已獲攬炒巴授權使用）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人哋北韓都做到 香港唔係做唔到呀嘛？</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共已經決定企硬，連溫和到咁既五大訴求都唔會接受。咁呢個政府仲有咩面代表人民<br />\n<br />\n擇個好日子揀個好地方，設立海外臨時政府<br />\n<br />\n目標係「要使國際社會廣泛相信港共政府為非法政權，爭取外國政府支持，替天行道，天滅中共」<br />\n「因應警察濫用暴力+濫捕事件於國際組織上追究」<br />\n<br />\n最後「推動香港進入real autonomy 嘅時代」<br />\n<br />\n因為而家我哋已經無嘢可以好輸，如果我哋就咁俾場運動完結，最後受害，被批鬥，被清算係每一個真。香港人。前線於是，和理非也如是。警察已經將文革係各中小學重演，唔駛好耐就會到其他界別。"},{"pid":"a166b0429ed65ffef3353a316c30ed744d2f9e90","tid":1567324,"uid":269428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:46:11.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4af9064b9f3992277c4394fb38dcc4524e839a84","tid":1567324,"uid":286839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d923b0198291beb0b65ddf95ac2faa28dcf4bf0","tid":1567324,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:39:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家係咪以為羸咗呀?<br />\n唔係嘅話就努力啲宣傳啦! <br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n9.15 英領<br />\n時間: 12點<br />\n<br />\n9.15 遊行<br />\n時間: 2點半<br />\n起點: 銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n終點: 遮打道行人專用區<br />\n<br />\n有幾點想講:<br />\n<br />\n1. <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins>遊行人數好重要</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n警方俾咗反對通知，如果你身邊朋友猶豫緊出唔出，甚至嗰個係你，請記住香港係有集會自由!但而家已經蕩然無存。<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人必需站出來捍衛香港嘅核心價值。Hong Kong is not China.</span><br />\n<br />\n2.<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> <ins>銀髮族扮演重要角色</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔好睇少銀髮族，佢地好關鍵! 警察其實好少搞銀髮族，所以人數多嘅話，佢地可以成為年青人嘅屏障。<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>勇武和理缺一不可</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n和理非手足請繼續和理非，因為今次遊行人數非常重要，我地要玩到五大訴求應承哂為止，絕對寸步不讓。<br />\n<br />\n勇武手足請繼續帶gear。保護好自己，保護好身邊手足，一個都不能少。隨時要準備同黑警搏鬥，但都要小心。唔好因戀戰而送頭。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武和理團結係運動繼續行落去嘅重要彈藥!</span><br />\n<br />\n4. <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins>嚴防休班警特襲</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家都如而家休班警配備警棍，隨時可以毆我地。但係我地絕對唔可以任人魚肉!<span style=\"color: red;\">所以我地需要提高警覺，千祈唔好落單。如果真係有手足俾人圍，一定要大嗌求助! 其他人務必救受困手足!</span><br />\n<br />\n5. <strong><ins>退場計劃 (Exit Plan)</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n黨鐵封站係基本動作。要順利退場，<span style=\"color: red;\">我地要變裝!將自己打扮成一個普通市民，隱藏於鬧市當中。大家遊行完可以行街、食飯、睇戲。而家唔係出街都犯法呀嘛?</span><br />\n總之盡量唔好俾啲狗有理由懷疑你參加集會。<br />\n<br />\n當大家撤緊時，和理非如果聽到有關防暴嘅消息時請保持冷静，唔好拔足狂奔，以免制造恐慌。<span style=\"color: red;\">大家可以急步行，退緊時盡量唔好嗌口號! 太嘈會傳達唔到現場訊息!!</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:46:12.000Z","msg":"推上熱門呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b46f36f43ffac1eb7572a9dcea4f46e77f44af6","tid":1567324,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:46:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1c337f758086c082f42525187045214c7e1876f3","tid":1567324,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:46:39.000Z","msg":"推行動post!!"},{"pid":"f0b806d2330b5234a3776e8f97cc24da6da8b42b","tid":1567324,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:47:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9190d2d7fbb404a1b4a0b895a99a95edc1cbbf35","tid":1567324,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:48:11.000Z","msg":"psuh"},{"pid":"955e42a5d9f25034fbd539ac7a03e1e31ba44a01","tid":1567324,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:51:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7c143524be6f95f51f65e7d1b30138cb0d6c4775","tid":1567324,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:51:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"041523f8437233a058